#: pygments.lexers.load_lexer_from_file:3
msgid ""
"This method expects a file located relative to the current working "
"directory, which contains a Lexer class. By default, it expects the Lexer to "
"be name CustomLexer; you can specify your own class name as the second "
"argument to this function."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../pygments/lexers/__init__.py:docstring of
#: pygments.lexers.load_lexer_from_file:8
